    "ArticleTitle": "Update of the 2009 Italian Pediatric Society Guidelines about management of fever in children.",
    "Pagination": {
      "StartPage": "1648",
      "EndPage": "1653.e3",
      "MedlinePgn": "1648-1653.e3"
